➜老马后又一位足坛巨星告别：意大利巨星保罗·罗西离世
http://www.sohu.com/a/437364827_116237	8339
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
